      <title>丰田成为亚洲最受做空的大盘股 - Hazeltree</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-becomes-asias-most-shorted-large-cap-stock-hazeltree-2024-03-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据公司 Hazeltree 周二的一份报告显示，汽车制造商丰田汽车公司 (Toyota Motor Corp) 超越武田制药 (Takeda Pharmaceutical)，成为 2 月份亚太地区对冲基金做空次数最多的大盘股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-becomes-asias-most-shorted-large-cap-stock-hazeltree-2024-03-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 14:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
