      <title>汽油、住房成本推动美国二月份通胀走高</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/gasoline-shelter-costs-lift-us-consumer-prices-february-2024-03-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于汽油和住房成本上涨，美国 2 月份消费者价格稳步上涨，这表明通货膨胀的粘性使人们对美联储是否会在 6 月份开始降息产生一些怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/gasoline-shelter-costs-lift-us-consumer-prices-february-2024-03-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 12:45:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
